Package: imageTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Remote Sensing Image Processing and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Vinícius D'Lucas Bezerra e Queiroz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Vinícius D'Lucas Bezerra e Queiroz <vinicius.dlucas@gmail.com>
Description: A set of tools for processing and analyzing remote sensing images, including functions for sampling raster data, creating shapefiles, classification algorithms,validating classifications, and calculating metrics. CMAP classifier is included.
Imports:sf,dplyr,raster,terra,reshape2,dplyr,stats,ggplot2,caret,fitdistrplus,MVN,scales,extrafont
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
